{"tid":2125102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天下圍中 澳反對北京南海主張","createTime":"2020-07-26T03:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T05:19:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6136d672701cf9ed1d47793d9694ccceda024e74","tid":2125102,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200726/3UTDTP7FO6QS3GH3GQWTSDWNWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200726%2F3UTDTP7FO6QS3GH3GQWTSDWNWM%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLhfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=be956762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200726%2F3UTDTP7FO6QS3GH3GQWTSDWNWM%2F&h=6177a448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200726/3UTDTP7FO6QS3GH3GQWTSDWNWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n天下圍中 澳反對北京南海主張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FMHqzJ2Ii_BeBEDDl3TbvioT7-0=/640x383/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZUNBYYHXKLK2GXFSW6CIM4XQQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFMHqzJ2Ii_BeBEDDl3TbvioT7-0%3D%2F640x383%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZUNBYYHXKLK2GXFSW6CIM4XQQE.jpg&h=dfe9b427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳洲的艦隻日前與中國對峙。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n繼美國指斥中國在南海的領土主張為「完全非法」，澳洲亦已跟隨美國，就南海問題表明中國的多個主張「沒有法律依據」，包括九段線及中國建設人工島。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲在本月23日提交該聲明給聯合國，聲明指：「澳洲拒絕中國在南海『長期歷史實踐』的主張，當中包括中國的『歷史權利』或『海事權利』以及中國對南海的利益。」聲明又指：「中國在南海劃定直線基線，連結海洋地形或『島嶼群』最外層地點，包括『四沙』群島、『大陸』群島或『偏遠』群島周圍，這些做法沒有法律依據。」<br />\n<br />\n澳洲是美國之後，首個宣稱中國在南海的行動屬於非法的國家。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印度增軍備 印尼完成軍演<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台駐美代表履新 自封「外交戰貓」<br />\n<br />\n近日與中國關係緊張的印度亦有抗中的軍事買賣，《印度時報》昨引述消息報道，印度已開展向美國購買六架美製P8波賽頓海上巡邏機的程序，售價約18億美元（約139億港元）。此外，印度亦希望向美國加快採購6架MQ9武裝無人機，以應對目前與中國的軍事對抗。<br />\n<br />\n南海附近另一個國家印尼亦有軍事行動。。。。。。。。。。。。《日經亞洲評論》報道指出，印尼的行動是故意展現武力，反對中國在南海主權主張。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/印度時報"},{"pid":"5d5b21417efffe82d9617e0531217c5a4319c5c6","tid":2125102,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654b2f077f8e067f67395559e4d53d27d8ee0a11","tid":2125102,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:08:52.000Z","msg":"澳洲係老美最堅實盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc8fb59164b98bca4a805af7d1e13f0de840ce6","tid":2125102,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f3f84cdc6889770d28117656f7784c1064d214","tid":2125102,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"支持中華亮劍共和國反擊！劍指坎培拉！"}]}